  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065770/extras/e1976fefd04b4f2b8f1942d43a8614d9.poster.avif?t=1725600191\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065770/extras/e1976fefd04b4f2b8f1942d43a8614d9.webm?t=1725600191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065770/extras/e1976fefd04b4f2b8f1942d43a8614d9.mp4?t=1725600191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Horde Combat Shooter</h2>Face endless waves of monstrous adversaries as you fight to survive and progress through difficult levels.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065770/extras/bf9e1d0bf38afeac62982464cd2759cd.poster.avif?t=1725600191\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065770/extras/bf9e1d0bf38afeac62982464cd2759cd.webm?t=1725600191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065770/extras/bf9e1d0bf38afeac62982464cd2759cd.mp4?t=1725600191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Roguelike Mechanics</h2>Each playthrough is unique! Explore procedurally generated environments, discover powerful weapons, and make strategic decisions to adapt to every game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065770/extras/e627f547b442dcb7e889b021c6294c74.poster.avif?t=1725600191\" width=690 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065770/extras/e627f547b442dcb7e889b021c6294c74.webm?t=1725600191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065770/extras/e627f547b442dcb7e889b021c6294c74.mp4?t=1725600191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Bullet-Hell Intensity</h2>Test your reflexes and precision amidst relentless bullet patterns and overwhelming odds.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Loot and Level-Up</h2>Collect valuable resources, level up your character, and unlock new abilities to enhance your chances of survival.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >20 Minutes of Thrills</h2>Each level presents a 20-minute time limit, adding an element of urgency and excitement to every session.<br><br>Prepare yourself for an epic journey through the apocalypse, where danger lurks around every corner. Can you conquer the horde and emerge as the ultimate survivor?",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065770/extras/e1976fefd04b4f2b8f1942d43a8614d9.poster.avif?t=1725600191\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065770/extras/e1976fefd04b4f2b8f1942d43a8614d9.webm?t=1725600191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065770/extras/e1976fefd04b4f2b8f1942d43a8614d9.mp4?t=1725600191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Horde Combat Shooter</h2>Face endless waves of monstrous adversaries as you fight to survive and progress through difficult levels.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065770/extras/bf9e1d0bf38afeac62982464cd2759cd.poster.avif?t=1725600191\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065770/extras/bf9e1d0bf38afeac62982464cd2759cd.webm?t=1725600191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065770/extras/bf9e1d0bf38afeac62982464cd2759cd.mp4?t=1725600191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Roguelike Mechanics</h2>Each playthrough is unique! Explore procedurally generated environments, discover powerful weapons, and make strategic decisions to adapt to every game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065770/extras/e627f547b442dcb7e889b021c6294c74.poster.avif?t=1725600191\" width=690 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065770/extras/e627f547b442dcb7e889b021c6294c74.webm?t=1725600191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065770/extras/e627f547b442dcb7e889b021c6294c74.mp4?t=1725600191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Bullet-Hell Intensity</h2>Test your reflexes and precision amidst relentless bullet patterns and overwhelming odds.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Loot and Level-Up</h2>Collect valuable resources, level up your character, and unlock new abilities to enhance your chances of survival.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >20 Minutes of Thrills</h2>Each level presents a 20-minute time limit, adding an element of urgency and excitement to every session.<br><br>Prepare yourself for an epic journey through the apocalypse, where danger lurks around every corner. Can you conquer the horde and emerge as the ultimate survivor?",
